snippet.title: BFI
snippet.description:
Welcome to the BFI, bringing you exclusive Screen Talks and Filmmaker Q&As from London's BFI Southbank cinema venue, access to one of the world's best moving picture archives, film trailers, highlights from our Film Festivals and original video content from new filmmaking talent.

We believe society needs stories. Film, television and the moving image bring them to life, helping us to connect and understand each other better. We share the stories of yesterday, search for the stories of today, and shape the stories of tomorrow.
